name: Taimanin Suit Outfit LoRA
description:
Taimanin Suit Outfit LoRA

LoRA request queue: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1DXjs-96citoEa4NPWWxm4o92kQyrJpgdXQGWQg65oiM/edit?usp=sharing

This model was trained using 102 images of various characters wearing a taimanin suit. Almost all of them were cosplays, meaning you won't get the original character faces. It was trained on the NAI model so it should work with most anime based models. This model used a decent amount of NSFW.

Recommended weight is between 0.7 and 0.9. It was specifically trained on the outfit, and not the faces or poses, so make sure to describe those in your prompt to not get weird faces. It is not perfect so it might require some inpainting. Sadly the covered nipples were slightly baked in, so you might need to inpaint those out.

Trigger word is Taimanin suit, which will give you a random variation. You can then add more stuff to get the one you want.

Example images were generated using AOM2 hard with 50 steps, then were upscaled on low strength with 150 steps.
